name: Oemah Arak
address: GF33+V78 BD. Telunwayah Berenang, Tri Eka Buana, Kec. Sidemen, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: Very beautiful restaurant! Super friendly staff, very helpful. Went above and beyond to help us! Even got us the coconut right from the tree. The food was very nice. Overall good experience!
review 2: The place is very nice, you only have to enter a little, it is very quiet and the style of the restaurant is very pleasant. The food and the attention of the staff is incredible, we tried a distillate that they prepare there and it was very good, totally recommended and hygienic.
review 3: Beautiful restaurant with a stunning view on the rice fields. They make very tasty traditional arak. They ladies are lovely and very kind. The food is delicious too! Stop here if you are visiting Gembleng waterfall!!!
review 4: Beautiful place and very welcoming owner. We had a great chat, drank few shots of Arak and we even bought a bottle. Unfortunately Arak we bought tasted like sewage and was totally different from one we tasted.
review 5: It doesnâ€™t get more authentic than this. Off the beaten path. Food and Arak not to be missed.
